{"tid":902570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有黨不用怕]港府重申外國議會不應干預香港內部事務","createTime":"2018-11-15T02:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T04:54:47.000Z","uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"920cc9c6bda131209424e8748c7a9c2cd8ace78b","tid":902570,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=327327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D327327&d=kik4d0YPBIva1UE5XH0I6wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d671a777\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D327327&h=1d8076cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=327327</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】美國美中經濟與安全審查委員會發表年度報告，指北京持續侵蝕香港政制、法治和言論自由，建議國會要求商務部檢視對港科技出口政策。特區政府發聲明，重申外國議會不應以任何形式干預特區內部事務。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府對報告感到遺憾，指結論偏頗，指控失實，自回歸以來一直嚴格按基本法實行港人治港，十分重視言論自由和新聞自由，任何港獨主張違反基本法，沒有討論空間，基本法指明香港是單獨關稅地區，特區一直致力執行戰略貿易管制，會一如既往繼續與美國保持緊密合作。<br />\n<br />\n美中經濟與安全審查委員會報告引用馬凱被拒續簽工作簽證、高鐵西九龍站、實施一地兩檢為例，形容香港自由持續受壓，慢慢喪失獨有法制，漸趨似內地城市，令香港失去成為美國重要伙伴的特點，而美國過去對港科技出口政策是基於將內地與香港，視為兩個獨立關稅地區。<br />\n<br />\n繼續企硬就算凍結資產都唔怕, 我們還有黨, 缺心跟黨走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacccd60949de35250d975f0ad5120e33c8e4d2c","tid":902570,"uid":84633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:17:45.000Z","msg":"但港府阻止對方咁做即係干預對方事務?"},{"pid":"73c78319b6400016923ccd82d13566bd2362ea77","tid":902570,"uid":176991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:18:58.000Z","msg":"人地國家點看待你係人地嘅內政喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e84bea0de068acdbf0c54d3e498dca921bf7241","tid":902570,"uid":81562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"美國國會出份report自己參考又關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那種真係支那種 自己走去干預人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a690defbe855cc6c36ea5aa057d7bd1f05c9fcb","tid":902570,"uid":12599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"人地政策係人地內政,港府同中方不應干預"},{"pid":"84e630f4a8a7c8d3f8be6ef1d2cc9369f351d6e2","tid":902570,"uid":31517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:20:38.000Z","msg":"連口吻都同大陸一樣"},{"pid":"ab74618c6562089ed4a718644bbdf8c9dae1abe4","tid":902570,"uid":22926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"係囉！<br />\n香港政府快啲叫美國取消「香港關係法」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606e3573649e29bd46a147156b66af2eeafae244","tid":902570,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181114/20545680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181114%2F20545680&d=kik4d0YPBIva1UE5XH0I6wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=85d645cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181114%2F20545680&h=62f1e32f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181114/20545680</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這份1992年的文件中，英方羅列了當年4月至5月期間，中方在不同國際場合及左報媒體發表認為1997年後香港就只屬中方內部事務的「罪狀」。</span>可能今天這種說法已是司空見慣，但當年對已跟中方「坐同一隻船」的英國，卻有需要預想若果跳船與不跳船的潛在對策，純粹以備不時之需。<br />\n<br />\n中共1992年已經當正主權移交之後國際就對香港冇監察權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d977177d3d52e2fd47a9947bb9ce29f06592a68e","tid":902570,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:21:58.000Z","msg":"單獨關稅區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11932039cc130a4338adb1073f1e3a97b91dd8f7","tid":902570,"uid":45098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"做咩調轉左黎講既<br />\n驚到語無倫次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38999663d570cebf10536cbee21ef4fda15a4384","tid":902570,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"想取消左關係法遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係干預你"},{"pid":"4c076ec88e77ee0606780f20c34965fd172b0ff8","tid":902570,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"基本法列明唔代表外國就要承認<br />\n一國大於兩制下，香港應該被視為中國城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9781fab9fbb43b3e63e8e4ba1d8264332972b1e5","tid":902570,"uid":39133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"人地要取消關係法駛唔駛問過你港府呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072720f613a81efaa3fadf466e9823ed1bf75036","tid":902570,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab74618c6562089ed4a718644bbdf8c9dae1abe4","tid":902570,"uid":22926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"係囉！<br />\n香港政府快啲叫美國取消「香港關係法」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"777：未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}